header.note: The source node in most cases contains the sample message as written by the developer. If it looks like a dot-delimitted string such as "form.label.firstname", then the developer has not provided a default message.

trans-unit.source: Previewed page is not based on a content item. Page Builder is working with limited set of features.
trans-unit.target: L'aperçu de la page n'est pas basé sur du contenu. Le fonctionnement du constructeur de page est limité.
